metadata.description:
The Shades of Gabriel is not just an NFT project, it's a testament to the strength and resilience of the human spirit. Gabriel's journey has been a difficult one, marked by the devastating impact of COVID and the relentless persistence of a brain infection caused by herpes.

But through it all, Gabriel has persevered, his unbreakable spirit shining through the darkness. Each shade in this project represents a different aspect of Gabriel's journey, from the pain and suffering to the moments of hope and triumph.

As you explore these shades, you'll feel the raw emotion and depth of Gabriel's experience. You'll see the strength that allowed him to keep fighting, even when the odds seemed insurmountable. And you'll be inspired by his courage in the face of unimaginable adversity.

The Shades of Gabriel is more than just an NFT project, it's a testament to the power of the human spirit. And it's a tribute to Gabriel, whose unwavering determination and resilience serve as a shining example to us all.
